      <title>以色列内塔尼亚胡因战争行为解雇国防部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/israel-s-netanyahu-fires-defense-minister-over-war-disagreements</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡解雇了国防部长约阿夫加兰特，称他们之间在处理与哈马斯和真主党的冲突问题上长期存在的分歧已经无法弥合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/israel-s-netanyahu-fires-defense-minister-over-war-disagreements</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 18:31:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克国防部长警告有人图谋夺权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/mozambique-s-defense-minister-warns-of-a-plot-to-seize-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克国防部长警告称，在该国有争议的选举之后，不明身份的人正准备试图夺取政权，而邻国南非则因边境爆发暴力抗议活动而关闭了一条重要的金属贸易路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/mozambique-s-defense-minister-warns-of-a-plot-to-seize-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 15:51:23 GMT</pubDate>
